\[\bm{X}_{i}^{k}-\mu_{k}\widetilde{\nabla}_{\mathcal{R}}f(\bm{X}_{i}^{k})-\bm{I} =(1-\mu_{k}\sigma)(\bm{X}_{i}^{k}-\bm{I})+\mu_{k}(\widetilde{\nabla}_{ \mathcal{R}}f(\bm{X}_{i})-\sigma(\bm{X}_{i}-\bm{I})),\]

